title: PS3 The Evil Within [ODE Fix]
description:
*NOT THE FULL GAME!

PS3 The Evil Within (BLES01916)

ODE Fix

This is a firmware 4.60 game. Copy and Replace file to play game on PS3s with firmware 4.55 or lower.

Step 1 - Download full PS3 The Evil Within (BLES01916) Game
Step 2 - Copy and Replace the PS3_GAME file with this one. Do Not Delete your PS3_GAME File!
Step 3 - Convert game back to ISO to play on ODE
